# Keep the sdist minimal and contamination-safe (added 2026-07-12).
# The test suite was built using the owner's real vault as example data, so it
# is not shipped in the distribution — it isn't needed to build/run the package,
# and shipping it once leaked a real term into the 0.16.0 sdist. The wheel never
# contained tests (only src/brain); this makes the sdist match.
prune tests
prune eval
prune docs
prune tools
prune packaging
prune overlay
prune templates
prune scripts
prune vault
prune dist
